dmca.title: DMCA (Copyright) Complaint to Google
dmca.body:
The following message has been automatically forwarded to your
address for consultation, based on the contents of the message.

Replies to this message will be returned to the Trakken system,
and not sent to the customer.  A customer service agent will review
the information you provide, and compose a response to the customer,
if necessary.

For more information on this ticket, click the link below:
http://trax/html/trax.html?ticket_id=827489145

Thanks for your help.

The text of the message follows, and the full message is attached.


Original Message Follows:
------------------------
From: isaac.rinsky@gmail.com

dmca_clarifications: Good Day,

A few days ago I published a new blog about skin whitening. In the blog I  
gathered all the information about that subject, using my professional  
abilities and knowledge (I am a clinical pharmacist) in order to introduce  
to the readers only reliable materials.
For some reason the blog does not appear in Google search and I have the  
impression that the blog is not promoted because of a complaint for  
copyright infringement.
I never received any such complaint, and I do not know why and for what.
To my knowledge I did not violated any copyrights, and if I did so, of  
course I will immediately download any such material (images or text).

I would appreciate to have your answer as soon as possible.

Best Regards,

Isaac Rinsky
